            A thematic recognition earned by completing 12 to 26 related activities. Prove sustained commitment in a focused area, without pursuing full Certification.
          </p>
          <span class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center text-[14px] font-medium text-seam-700">
            See Seal &rarr;
          </span>
        </div>

        <a href="/certification" class="group rounded-2xl border border-warm-200/60 bg-white p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col transition-all duration-300 hover:border-warm-300 hover:shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-[13px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-warm-500 mb-4">Step 3</p>
